The CCE is structured into three interlocking pillars, ensuring all data is
validated, secured, and stored with high fidelity and zero-latency
enforcement.
1. The Intelligence Layer: G-NEXUS CORE

This is the analytical and generative engine, focused on transforming raw,
noisy data into actionable, high-signal intelligence.
Component Prototype Function Architectural Proof
