grounded, multi-modal analysis and delivers structured reports (e.g., Q4
financial projections). Confirmed the *2-Step Decoupling Protocol* for
reliable LLM output.
*Aether Sentinel* Aether Sentinel Model Core Proactive threat detection and
immediate, structured risk scoring of incoming data streams. Confirmed
successful generation of actionable JSON for instantaneous enforcement. 2.
The Enforcement Layer: G-SHIELD SYSTEM

